{"tid":194943,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得自己係隻鐵達尼號沉船⋯⋯","createTime":"2017-04-10T10:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T17:52:01.000Z","uid":98542,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"937b466f43df0a27055ffcb32b52317496a33d61","tid":194943,"uid":98542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:19:19.000Z","msg":"小弟拍拖兩次<br />\n兩次都係唔夠三個星期就散<br />\n重要重傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且每次追親女仔<br />\n都係食檸檬收場<br />\n一係唔係就係肥婆、player係咁搵我<br />\n我問我D 女仔frd同兄弟<br />\n「我係咪好樣衰？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n全部回答就係咁安慰我<br />\n話咩「唔係」、「仲靚仔過D韓星」⋯⋯<br />\n但正正因爲呢D説話<br />\n搞到我自信過高，成日瀨野<br />\n我真心想問各位巴絲打<br />\n我知道連登各位有嗰句，講嗰句<br />\n我想知我個樣到底係柒定過得去<br />\n至少俾我知道自己究竟咩斤兩<br />\n唔好再「癩蛤蟆想食天鵝」<br />\n如果各位巴絲打想小弟出相<br />\n小弟會出相 (可能會整污糟各位對眼，sorry)<br />\n但請各位當小弟過眼雲煙算<br />\n唔好係街同小弟相認或者攞我幅相黎玩<br />\n小弟唔係咩紅人<br />\n冇咩好玩㗎咋<br />\n拜託<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7885a6c0d674129a4af0fca92cc0f7203c5db3","tid":194943,"uid":62822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:20:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9ac1eb0ad77a00c1bd795aad41d24ea97beaeb97","tid":194943,"uid":44551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:21:42.000Z","msg":"無相點討論"},{"pid":"81c75064465eac4ecaca436c4c767d2ec4485334","tid":194943,"uid":9034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:21:49.000Z","msg":"要相"},{"pid":"4adbacd6ed185a5dda32820304f498d10ceed48b","tid":194943,"uid":88263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:22:39.000Z","msg":"圖？"},{"pid":"85dba4dcfcb1216a5feaabe316498413a7f58a3b","tid":194943,"uid":53297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T10:23:37.000Z","msg":"相<img src